Art,<br><br>
By God I think you have it!! Or did someone else say that?  That definition will do.  Both of them.  Lets go deeper into the realm of nothing.<br><br>
Existence so specific that no other level exists.  No depth, width, length, a mere point in space that conceives no other existence.  That which hears, but believes all it hears is a generation within its own mind.  It questions its self, answers its self, becomes trapped in its omnipotence.  A nothing in the vast plane of discovery.  All else is heresy.<br><br>
Single dimensional existence in a multi-dimensional world.  Most important, no event horizon, it need not and cannot exert influence outside its own realm.<br><br>
Venture not to this point and you can forget it ever was.<br><br>
You are right Art,  The night is a prowling kind of night.<br><br>
SW
